#  Cumulative Task - Pipeline DevOps AWS

**Node.js 21** • **GitHub Actions** → **ECR** → **EC2** • **Docker Compose**

## 🎯 Architecture

Git Push → GitHub Actions → Build → ECR Push↓EC2 ← SSH + Docker Compose → Live App : http://51.20.114.208:8080


##  Fonctionnalités

- ✅ **CI/CD** : Auto-deploy sur `main`
- ✅ **Containerisé** : Docker + Node.js 21 + app.js
- ✅ **AWS ECR** : Private registry versioning
- ✅ **EC2 Production** : Ubuntu + Docker Compose
- ✅ **Sécurisé** : AWS Secrets + SSH Keys

## 📋 Workflow GitHub Actions

```yaml
# .github/workflows/deploy.yml
- Configure AWS credentials (secrets)
- docker build → coursera/cumulative-task:latest
- docker push ECR
- SSH EC2 → docker compose up -d --force-recreate

##  Déploiement live

